News.Title: MOS Utility Q3 Net Profit Jumps 75% to ₹49M
News.Summary: MOS Utility reported strong Q3 performance with consolidated net profit rising 75% YoY to ₹49 million, while revenue grew 31% to ₹1.7 billion compared to previous year.

News.Title: Mos Utility Partners With My Mudra Fincorp Limited for Financial Services Transformation in India
News.Summary: Mos Utility has entered into a partnership with My Mudra Fincorp Limited to transform financial services in India. The collaboration focuses on promoting financial inclusion and expanding product offerings through JC Ventures' CSP (Customer Service Point) network.

News.Title: Mos Utility Partners With DigiAsia Corp To Expand Financial Inclusion In Indonesia And India
News.Summary: Mos Utility has formed an agreement with DigiAsia Corp to boost financial inclusion in Indonesia and India. The partnership focuses on enhancing branchless banking services and developing AI tools for agents to support these initiatives.
